This is a Receipt creator.
It creates receipts by writing an predefined template. 
The app has 3 views, the login screen, the receipt creating screen and the receipt viewer.
The log in uses bcrypt as authentication.
The database that keeps the receipts are sqlite.
The receipts are stored in a csv and can be viewed
In the receipt creator, you can create receipts, print receipts and view receipts that have already been created.